# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Groq API key — used for the chat LLM (free tier, no credit card).
# Get one at: https://console.groq.com/keys
# Copy this file to ".env.local" and paste your key below.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
GROQ_API_KEY=your_groq_api_key_here

# Optional: override the Groq chat model.
# Defaults to llama-3.3-70b-versatile (free, fast, high quality).
# GROQ_MODEL=llama-3.3-70b-versatile

# Optional: override the local embedding model (runs on your machine, no key).
# EMBEDDING_MODEL=Xenova/all-MiniLM-L6-v2

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Upstash Vector — REQUIRED for serverless hosting (Vercel), optional locally.
# When BOTH are set, the app stores vectors and does embeddings in Upstash
# instead of the local model + in-memory store. Leave blank for local/Render.
#
# Setup: https://console.upstash.com → Vector → Create Index →
#        choose an embedding model (e.g. BAAI/bge-small-en-v1.5) → copy the
#        REST URL and REST TOKEN here.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# UPSTASH_VECTOR_REST_URL=https://your-index.upstash.io
# UPSTASH_VECTOR_REST_TOKEN=your_upstash_rest_token
